wood.description: www.arborupcycle.comLIVE EDGE WOOD SLABS FOR SALE, ROUNDS, OVALS, AND MORE.FREE WOOD SCRAPS always available!Products :- Live Edge Slabs (wet, dried)- Various wood pieces and tree parts (incl. stumps, branches, etc.)Services :- Custom milling (including dimensional lumber milling)- Log/reclaimed wood hauling- Planing and Surfacing (Free scrap wood available at the warehouse from 9-2 daily M-F (only during these hours).  Pieces perfect for small woodworkers or people who want to take their try with wood. Grab it for free.)Arbor Upcycle is the only company in San Francisco dedicated to salvaging and milling downed trees in San Francisco. After a tree is removed due to storm damage or urban development Arbor Upcycle will strive to salvage the tree for its timber. The tree is then milled into slabs on-site or at our warehouse. The 3” wood slabs are then stickered and set aside to cure until they are stable enough to build with or sell.Every piece is identified by its true species and neighborhood in San Francisco where the tree once stood.Arbor Upcycle is not only salvaging valuable timber and sequestering carbon off-gassing but also reclaiming some of San Francisco’s oldest residing residents and in doing so is preserving SF’s heritage in the face of a rapidly changing urban landscape.Next time you need a tree removed or see a tree being removed we hope you think of Arbor Upcycle and our mission to sustainably manage our urban forest and contribute to our community.    http://arborupcycle.com/

fast.name: 2004 Mazda 6 Sport - Fast & Reliable
fast.description: Unfortunately it is time to pass on my absolutely amazing 2004 Mazda 6 Sport Hatchback! It is in great condition, serviced frequently and well taken care of by our local and trusted mechanic at Advanced Auto in Santa Cruz. Runs perfectly, drove it to Yosemite last week and Anaheim about a month ago with absolutely no problems. Great gas mileage and a comfortable ride for road trips. Always received premium gas and oil changes every 3,000 miles.Completely upgraded the sound system with a 12inch kicker subwoofer and new speakers and amp (Sounds Incredible). I also put in a touchscreen Pioneer center display that is bluetooth capable and has a usb hookup for your phone to charge and play music. I also installed a back-up camera! This car has really been well taken care of and I am sad to see it go but I am in need of something a bit bigger. There are some signs of age as you can see in the seats and body and the text in the center screen is starting to fade a bit (See Photos). But these minor cosmetic blemishes are truly only aesthetic and do not take away from how amazing this car drives. There are no mechanical issues at all, sometimes a bit of oil does burn off the engine resulting in a smell but we have confirmed with our mechanic that there is no underlying issue associated with this. It’s fast and reliable and will get you where you need to go in comfort and style.The price is $5250 Obo and please feel free to reach out with ANY questions or to schedule a test drive!

famous.description: Pretty little soprano, nice build with super-thin mahogany laminate, but with a sound that will rival most sold-wood ukes. Extremely light, with excellent projection and beautiful resonance. The FS-1 is a Japanese build, identical to the Kiwaya KS-1, but sold only to the Japanese market. Tiny scratch on the headstock, mark on the first fret - see the photos for detail. One-of-a-kind cloth gig bag included. Reasonable offers are welcome.

famous.name: Klon Centaur Professional Overdrive (Horsie)
famous.description: At Keith Holland Guitars in Los Gatos, CA, we painstakingly vet both our new and used instruments to make sure we only present instruments of the highest quality.  All of our instruments, old and new, are set up in our world-class repair shop before we display them in our showroom or advertise them online. When you buy from Keith Holland Guitars, you can rest assured that you're in good hands and that your instrument will be ready to play out of the box.Finnegan's Wake:Ever since Bill Finnegan created the Klon in the early 90's, pedal makers have been scrambling to replicate the magical clear transparent overdrive effect made famous by the pedal. Often imitated and rarely equaled, the Klon remains one of the most talked about pedals of all time. A shroud of mystery continually to surrounds the infamous overdrive. Many strong words have been exchanged between pedal builders, armchair scholars and professional musicians, who spend countless hours a discussing (or debating) just what particular component makes the pedal so good. The black goop, an epoxy resin that obscures the pedal's circuit, only adds to the mystery.All hype aside, its really a great sounding pedal. Its simple, easy to use and extremely versatile. It can act as a simple clean boost or used to get more dirt into your sound. It is a worthwhile investment for someone with a great sounding amp who would like to push it into overdrive territory without losing the natural tone of the amp and guitar. This specific Klon has the Horsie decal and a really low serial # at 492This particular pedal is in Good Condition. There is some scratching and wear to the front and sides of the enclosure and substantial scratching to the bottom. It has been lovingly used and studied by its two principal owners and has been in and around our store's possession ever since Keith was a dealer back in the day.

famous.name: Vintage '65 Fender Super Reverb 45-Watt 4x10" Guitar Combo Amp
famous.description: Selling a vintage '65 Fender Super Reverb 2 Channel 40-Watt 4x10 Guitar Combo Amp.This is an incredibly clean example of this amp.The amp is in fantastic working condition and has that classic warm super reverb tone that you can only really get with an all original vintage amp like this.Was recently went through by an amp tech and has a clean bill of health with a 3 prong power cord also installed!Built in July of 1965 in Fullerton, California.Comes loaded with 4 - '65/'66 Jensen C10Q speakersLoaded with NOS Vintage GE 6L6 power tubes, Rectifier tube, and reissue mix of Groove and EHX preamp tubesOriginal Vinyl Cover and Footswitch included!Please, serious inquiries only!Will only respond to emails with a name and phone number!No Trades!Thanks!OverviewThe Fender Super Reverb 45-watt tube combo guitar amplifier was offered in a blackface finish between 1964 and 1967, although some early silverface finished units still had blackface circuitry. Well-known for its scooped mids, the Super Reverb features the same design as the Fender Super, but with the addition of built-in reverb and tremolo effects as well as four 10 speakers. Famous Super Reverb players include Johnny Marr, Stevie Ray Vaughan, Robben Ford, and Derek Trucks.
